en: In this list you can see the current adverts. If you find a match, you can just go ahead an write this person a message.
You could not find a matching advert? Just enlist your own tandem-wish.
How good can you speek your requested Language?

People who are interested can now contact you through our portal. We will forward any request with the contact details to you. Then it is up to you to decide if to get into direkt contact.

For the first meetings we recommend one of our meeting suggestions. You can find them on our homepage.

We wish you good luck and a lots of fun at the %s Language Tandem!

Best regards

The %s Language Tandem Team
